{"tid":1056714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[TWICE彩瑛性感肉照照片無故洩露,」請保護藝人的私生活!","createTime":"2019-03-11T11:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T18:22:40.000Z","uid":88491,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a284478b34798d6b816f231f90faaa8c57d3876","tid":1056714,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"【osen】[TWICE彩瑛照片無故洩露,」請保護藝人的私生活!」]11日據媒體報道,#TWICE[超話]#成員#孫彩瑛[超話]#正因照片無故洩露而備受困擾.彩瑛通過組合官方ins上傳了一張照片並表示「我沒有上傳過的照片是從哪裡上傳的呢?很害怕.請不要再做那樣的事情了.」在公開的照片中是彩瑛身著比基尼在海邊休息的模樣.<br />\n<br />\n據悉,彩瑛自己都沒有上傳過的照片被人獲取後擅自洩露,這是充分可以被看作為犯罪的行為.特別是彩瑛直接表露出的恐懼感讓粉絲們也非常擔心.目前,粉絲們正在通過官方SNS的回帖提出「請保護藝人」,「請採取法律措施」等意見.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjFyHxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjFyHxC.png&h=7fafe5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db3824223a4fe7a8739a468bd60e61012ffcc880","tid":1056714,"uid":76098,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"實係佢個仆街隊友做"},{"pid":"96c65a9ef7685ea1de3442dd2612f2914a5c2bfa","tid":1056714,"uid":179051,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6501fe17da262af58df948b72393de11402b4094","tid":1056714,"uid":173631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"大波過heidi<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2AyHz0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2AyHz0.jpg&h=b77a2907&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85f5690eda4b17be9d33c95e7dd47d9962196214","tid":1056714,"uid":173631,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWQOwtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWQOwtZ.jpg&h=1dbd387d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sh9cdHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t